node.text:
@sydney_sweeney is on our podcast this week! Our August cover star talks everything from #TheWhiteLotus, to working with @iamhalsey, and even her unexpected hobby of rebuilding classic cars. Tap the link in bio to listen and subscribe. #WhoWhatWearPod

node.text:
We chatted with @jodiemcomer, star of @killingeve and @freeguymovie, about her best-kept beauty and wellness secrets, including tips she’s picked up from her makeup artists, @babskymakeup and @hungvanngo, and whether or not she takes inspiration from Villanelle for her IRL looks. Tap the link in our bio to read more. #Unfiltered
